Seven Oaks International Incsaid it has formed a new 80 pct owned subsidiary called SevenOaks Direct Inc to offer a full line of telemarketing services.    It said Seven Oaks direct management will own the remaining20 pct.    The company said initial costs connected with the startupoof a new Memphis, Tenn., marketing center for Seven Oaks directmay hurt earnings slightly in the first half of the year endingin April 1988, but Seven Oaks Direct should operate at no worsethan breakeven for fiscal 1988 as a whole. Reuter&#3;